The paper deals with neural network algorithms and their implementation on dedicated hardware systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also discusses the performance of these algorithms, which suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of neural networks in computer vision (cs.CV) and control systems (cs.SY), which are also possible categories.
